body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to us at Fast Auto Sales. My name is Wayne Robinson, one of our customer service representatives. May I please have your name?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Teresa. To assist you further, could you please provide me with your date of birth in the format of two eight zero three one nine nine zero?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's zero seven two six one nine eight zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Teresa. Additionally, may I also have the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's seven eight five two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing that information. We value your privacy and assure you that it is strictly confidential. Is there anything else you would like to share or discuss today, Teresa?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I appreciate that. I may feel a bit nervous about sharing personal details, but I'm glad to know it's secure. No, that's all for now.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing your concerns, Teresa. Your security is important to us, and we're here to address any worries you may have. If there's anything else you need assistance with in the future, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time today.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you, Wayne. I appreciate your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Teresa. Have a wonderful day.
